sampler.prompt: List main symptoms for a patient aged {age} diagnosed with {diagnosis}, in 1-2 short phrases.
Provide vital signs (BP, HR, Temp) for a {age}-year-old patient with {diagnosis} in a concise structured string.
Write a concise clinical note for a {age}-year-old patient from {city} diagnosed with {diagnosis}. Include presenting complaint and suggested next steps.
Write a short realistic {rating}-star customer review for a {category} item priced at {price}.
